coach_id.help:
Select the "Employee" who is the coach of this employee.
The "Coach" has no specific rights or responsibilities by default.
coach_id.name: coach_id

tz.help: This field is used in order to define in which timezone the resources will work.
tz.name: tz

employee_type.help: The employee type. Although the primary purpose may seem to categorize employees, this field has also an impact in the Contract History. Only Employee type is supposed to be under contract and will have a Contract History.
employee_type.name: employee_type

badge_ids.help: All employee badges, linked to the employee either directly or through the user
badge_ids.name: badge_ids

direct_badge_ids.help: Badges directly linked to the employee
direct_badge_ids.name: direct_badge_ids

leave_manager_id.help:
Select the user responsible for approving "Time Off" of this employee.
If empty, the approval is done by an Administrator or Approver (determined in settings/users).
leave_manager_id.name: leave_manager_id

remaining_leaves.help: Total number of paid time off allocated to this employee, change this value to create allocation/time off request. Total based on all the time off types without overriding limit.
remaining_leaves.name: remaining_leaves

allocation_used_count.string: Total number of days off used
allocation_used_count.name: allocation_used_count

show_leaves.string: Able to see Remaining Time Off
show_leaves.name: show_leaves
